    22	```text
    23	pose: 2.0 0 0.5 0 -1.57079632679 0
    24	```
    25	
    26	This puts the target in front of the x500 smoke model and rotates the marker
    27	plane to face the forward camera.
    28	
    29	## Pose Node
    30	
    31	Run:
    32	
    33	```bash
    34	ros2 launch aerial_manip_vision tag_target_pose.launch.py
    35	```
    36	
    37	The node subscribes to:
    38	
    39	| Topic | Type | Notes |
    40	| --- | --- | --- |
    41	| `/vision/front/image_raw` | `sensor_msgs/msg/Image` | Front camera image from the ROS/Gazebo bridge. |
    42	| `/vision/front/camera_info` | `sensor_msgs/msg/CameraInfo` | Camera intrinsics used by OpenCV pose estimation. |
    43	
    44	The node publishes:
    45	
    46	| Topic | Type | Frame |
    47	| --- | --- | --- |
    48	| `/vision/target_pose` | `geometry_msgs/msg/PoseStamped` | `uav/camera_link` using OpenCV camera optical axes. |
    49	| `/vision/target_pose_in_uav_frame` | `geometry_msgs/msg/PoseStamped` | `uav/base_link` using FLU axes. |
    50	
    51	The camera optical to UAV FLU conversion is:
    52	
    53	```text
    54	uav_x = camera_z
    55	uav_y = -camera_x
    56	uav_z = -camera_y
    57	```
    58	
