+Changed behavior:
+- scripts/stop_stack.sh now terminates both known Gazebo default.sdf command forms, PX4 SITL, and Micro XRCE-DDS udp4:8888 processes after killing known tmux sessions.
+- scripts/start_stack.sh records STACK_READY readiness status and supports STACK_SMOKE_ONLY=1 for bounded readiness checks that clean up immediately.
+- scripts/run_regression_demo_10.sh supports DEMO10_MODE=live-smoke, verifies readiness before full live Demo 10 nodes, cleans up on live failures, and keeps DEMO10_MODE=auto on dry-run.
+- Demo 10 dry-run now sets PYTHONPATH for local aerial_manip_eval, aerial_manip_control, and aerial_manip_vision sources.
+
