+Known risks:
+- Full DEMO10_MODE=live was not run; Task 025 documentation still says live ros2_control prerequisites are missing, so Demo 10 remains on the current high-level UAV bridge, placeholder target, and synthetic arm path.
+- The broad required pgrep pattern can match unrelated command lines containing px4 in paths or log names; the tighter stack-process pattern had no real process matches.
